{"tid":137151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北 韓 以 高 射 炮 處 決 5 名 高 級 官 員","createTime":"2017-02-27T14:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T12:03:13.000Z","uid":48093,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6706827cd4b5a3e2d7ce2db1570ae277883cc063","tid":137151,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T14:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1316124_1_L_20170227225727.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1316124_1_L_20170227225727.jpg&h=cd872e85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南韓情報機構表示，北韓以防空高射炮，處決5名高級安全官員，因為他們提供錯誤報告，激怒領袖金正恩。<br />\n<br />\n5人包括最近被革職的國家安全保衛相金元弘。<br />\n<br />\n目前不清楚錯誤的報告詳情，南韓方面亦未說明如何取得相關資訊。"},{"pid":"d503d7f82892dbae87569397687136afe66709b0","tid":137151,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:02:35.000Z","msg":"係唔係同金正男既死有關??<br />\n<br />\n因為呢五個官員 下令殺人之後, 有咁多手尾要跟, 又有四個特務被捉, 引起一連串外交/國際風波<br />\n<br />\n所以殺鳩佢地??"},{"pid":"1583a911d97f1f96a8fcd0ec8c05e33583d0018b","tid":137151,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:04:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5c385483140c93592a5cdcd66fba56ed9230924","tid":137151,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57bd6020b81ef581a1dc150685869c37a5562732","tid":137151,"uid":48442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:23:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"17887071bd28a01d5cafe0b4c7080b98467cc8bb","tid":137151,"uid":14423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:28:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da579b2bd171ffb6076ab8e53c47c626b8b2239","tid":137151,"uid":408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:28:52.000Z","msg":"<