不死，當場放生。大多受蚊刑者，皆撐不到黎明，便渾身浮腫，一命嗚呼。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/382lvpy.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fhistory%2F382lvpy.html&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT1%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=b11d8015\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/382lvpy.html</a></blockquote><br />\n搞到身好痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇咁勁，YouTube 有套裸體亞瑪遜，講一男一女衫都冇咁去求生，其中一集講兩條友點唔到火，夜蚊俾蚊針到傻，啲蚊又係一團一團咁黎<br />\n但根本冇乜大礙"},{"pid":"b475a2e84936995a332c180228bb8536af9b6647","tid":137151,"uid":6523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T01:30:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇得卡通多<br />\n以為裝個人落大炮射佢出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 我都以為係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 我以為係掛個人上炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3951761820672867291a754ed32f8c03a0456af0","tid":137151,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T01:35:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我冇睇過犬決，但火燒好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw咩叫犬決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n放個人入去個籠到，籠入面有一百隻餓左三日三夜既狗</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咁變態</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊撚到可以隨時搵到一百隻餓左三日三夜嘅狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n兩隻都死啦</blockquote><br />\n北韓搵隻飽狗難d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blo