n<br />\n你不如話一走了之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係有創意，蚊刑都有，咁蜂刑咪仲刺激？"},{"pid":"b40d82feb28130d3d5a67c61336b617d85cdf824","tid":137151,"uid":22374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T04:07:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>[quote][quote]寧願比高射一下秒都好過犬決同比火燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n犬決真係恐怖片嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我冇睇過犬決，但火燒好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw咩叫犬決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n放個人入去個籠到，籠入面有一百隻餓左三日三夜既狗</blockquote><br />\n最後 佢出返黎成為左武林高手</blockquote><br />\n你想我練打狗棒法，都要比支棍我先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n捉老納入去煮左100隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa6770df69353d416ed2b64e18f4d5b05aadb263","tid":137151,"uid":34971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T04:45:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>蚊刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蚊刑，顧名思義，就是用蚊子叮。讓人把罪犯衣服扒光，然後縛了，划船送到河心，看守守在四旁，坐在吊了帳子的船上。受刑者如若天明五時身亡，罪有應得；如若命大不死，當場放生。大多受蚊刑者，皆撐不到黎明，便渾身浮腫，一命嗚呼。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/382lvpy.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fhistory%2F382lvpy.html&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT1%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=b11d8015\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/382lvpy.html</a></blockquote><br />\n搞到身好痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇咁勁，YouTube 有套裸體亞瑪遜，講一男一女衫都冇咁去求生，其中一集講兩條友點唔到火，夜蚊俾蚊針到傻，啲蚊又係一團一團咁黎<br />\n但根本冇乜大礙</blockquote><br />\n <br />\nnaked and afraid"},{"pid":"3811731efcb670d44d5ea78f3891cbecbe9da474","tid":137151,"uid":52719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:26:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>蚊刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蚊刑，顧名思義，就是用蚊子叮。讓人把罪犯衣服扒光，然後縛了，划船送到河心，看守守在四旁，坐在吊了帳子的船上。受刑者如若天明五時身亡，罪有應得；如若命大不死，當場放生。大多受蚊刑者，皆撐不到黎明，便渾身浮腫，一命嗚呼。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/382lvpy.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fhistory%2F382lvpy.html&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT1%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=b11d8015\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/382lvpy.html</a></blockquote><br />\n搞到身好痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇咁勁，YouTube 有套裸體亞瑪遜，講一男一女衫都冇咁去求生，其中一集講兩條友點唔到火，夜蚊俾蚊針到傻，啲蚊又係一團一團咁黎<br />\n但根本冇乜大礙</blockquote><br />\n <br />\nnaked and afraid</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去求生被比蚊 痕都有得R<br />\n被蚊咬一野無得R 有幾難受<br />\n你再想象下你全身都好痕但係唔比你做任何動作避或者躲避...<br />\n<br />\n似係折磨你既神經系統 多過因為蚊會針到死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387350768eabc0672877375caf2864330a73744b","tid":137151,"uid":64896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T06:19:21.000Z","msg":"犬決有無片睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b507cff06feaf8bc484100aa98ab8d51e1c6f1","tid":137151,"uid":33422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T06:23:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>寧願比高射一下秒都好過犬決同比火燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></bloc